name: Breast Poking
description:
This is a LoRA to generate Breast poking.

  • I suggest using this at 1-1.5 weight for best results but make sure to always play around with the weight.

  • It was generated and only tested using AOM3 A1,AbyssOrangeMix2 - Hardcore

Always add this to the prompt to activate it: breast poke, poking

All pictures were upscaled in img2imag using these settings:

  • Control net 1.1 tile

  • Upscaler: 4x-Ultrasharp

Known Issues (As of now)

  • cant always generate the hand poking on breast so try to keep your prompt simple
